<media:description>Vidhya Srinivasan seated on a green couch.</media:description>
<description>&lt;img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-uniblog-publish-prod/images/Retouched_Final_copy.max-600x600.format-webp.webp"&gt;Google VP Vidhya Srinivasan shares how Google is reimagining commercial experiences to be fluid, assistive and personal in 2026.</description>
